    dc:description "FIGURE 15. Janaira platyoura sp. nov. Holotype female (P. 81231): A, body, lateral view (pereopods II – VII missing); B, body, dorsal view. Paratype female (P. 81233): C, right antennula; D, left mandible; E, right mandible; E, left maxillula with detail of distal margin of lateral lobe." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/198212/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.198213>
    dc:description "FIGURE 16. Janaira platyoura sp. nov. Paratype female (P. 81233): A, paragnath; B, left maxilliped with detail of endite distal margin; C, left maxilla; D, left pereopod I. Paratype male (P. 81234): E, left pereopod I." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/198213/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.198214>
    dc:description "FIGURE 17. Janaira platyoura sp. nov. Paratype female (P. 81233): A, right pereopod II; B, left pereopod VII; C, left uropod; D, operculum; E, right pleopod III. Paratype male (P. 81234): F, pleopod I, ventral view; G, right pleopod II." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/198214/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.198217>
    dc:description "FIGURE 20. Distribution of Janaira platyoura sp. nov. in the Batemans Bay region of New South Wales, Australia." ;
